---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="Ledger Donjon is the security research team at Ledger. Learn about our mission and expertise.">
  <Hero title="About the Donjon" size="sm" />
  
  <section class="content">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="lead">
        Ledger Donjon is the security research team at Ledger.
      </p>
      
      <div class="intro-text">
        <p>
          Its main mission is to improve the security of Ledger's products. From time to time, 
          the team also works on improving the security of the ecosystem.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          Punctually, the Donjon runs external security audit/consultancy.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <h2>Fields of Expertise</h2>
      
      <div class="expertise-grid">
        <div class="expertise-card">
          <div class="expertise-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Software Security</h3>
          <p>Firmware analysis, reverse engineering, vulnerability research, and secure development practices.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="expertise-card">
          <div class="expertise-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Hardware Security</h3>
          <p>Side-channel attacks, fault injection, chip decapsulation, and physical security assessment.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="expertise-card">
          <div class="expertise-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Cryptography</h3>
          <p>Protocol analysis, implementation review, and cryptographic algorithm assessment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2>Open Source</h2>
      
      <div class="intro-text">
        <p>
          The Donjon believes in open-source. We open-source most of our internal attack tools 
          to help the security community.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <a href="https://github.com/ledger-donjon" class="github-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="24" height="24">
          <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
        </svg>
        Visit Ledger Donjon on GitHub
      </a>
      
      <p class="cta-text">Pull requests are welcome!</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style lang="scss">
  .content {
    padding: var(--space-12) 0;
  }
  
  .lead {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }
  
  .intro-text {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    
    p {
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }
  }
  
  h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-4);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  
  .expertise-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-6);
    margin: var(--space-8) 0;
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
  
  .expertise-card {
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    transition: all var(--transition-normal);
    
    &:hover {
      border-color: var(--color-accent-primary);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-glow);
    }
    
    h3 {
      font-size: var(--text-lg);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    }
    
    p {
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
      margin: 0;
    }
  }
  
  .expertise-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--color-accent-glow);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    
    svg {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      color: var(--color-accent-primary);
    }
  }
  
  .github-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-6);
    background: var(--color-bg-tertiary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
    text-decoration: none;
    
    &:hover {
      background: var(--color-bg-hover);
      border-color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  }
  
  .cta-text {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
  }
</style>
